++ On Demand Friendliness

ODF means that the [PhysicalEndpoint] of [Representations] should be MachineReadable format and the friendless rendition of HumanReadable should be only be achieved through LogicalEndpoint.
    * ODF uses up less [Resources] and allows more IndepthData to be stored.
    * Difficult to modify or read
    * Can result in DatalessTemplates and AvoidObviousTemplates
    * Reduces [Directness] of UI but increases internal Directness
